{"tid":822810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【山竹襲港】高鐵西九巴士站首日啟用 颶風「吹響」警鐘","createTime":"2018-09-16T13:29:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T13:29:41.000Z","uid":38666,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"607c44de10ef76af370447aca331a56a5fff0143","tid":822810,"uid":38666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T13:29:41.000Z","msg":"強颱風「山竹」不單吹得港人頭都痛，也壞了一場好事。本應今日啟用的高鐵西九龍站巴士總站，因為八號風球已經於清晨懸掛關係，至今沒有一架巴士夠膽駛入車站；站內警報鐘聲一直長響，在場的工人表示是因為風力太強，「吹到佢響。」<br />\n西九龍巴士總站啟用後，會有11條巴士線遷入，不過因為颱風關係，車站啟用後沒有巴士停泊。站內的車長休息室亦已關好門，及貼上牛皮膠紙。<br />\n現場有數名工人在休息，其中一人表示，至今沒有行人路過，相信原因是接駁巴士站至港鐵站的天橋仍未啟用有關。<br />\n<br />\n九巴早前表示，站內沒有洗手間，其後運輸署發稿還擊指，是設有洗手間的。但記者現場所見，洗手間是設於站外地方，由站頭行去，有近200米距離。而廁所也受風暴吹襲，滿地樹葉，滿目瘡痍。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">港鐵柯士甸站前往高鐵西九站的出口水浸</span>，有工人在場施工。<br />\n港鐵回覆承認，西九龍站內有<span style=\"color: red;\">個別位置輕微「滴水」</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">整體大致正常</span>，重申西九龍站設計符合標準，可在本月29日通車。  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180916/large/1537084044_ab8b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180916%2Flarge%2F1537084044_ab8b.jpg&h=57f0749d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180916/small/1537084044_2154.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180916%2Fsmall%2F1537084044_2154.jpg&h=257852bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180916/58688505\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180916%2F58688505&d=fuqJwH1o5lKpd4H2CyNvGhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=4e289b77\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180916%2F58688505&h=6cbd6e66\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180916/58688505</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}